[Java convert hex to decimal](https://www.flowerbrackets.com/java-convert-hex-to-decimal/)

Java program to convert hexadecimal to decimal

We are using Integer.parseInt() method to convert hexadecimal to decimal parses string argument as a signed integer in the radix specified by the second argument.

Here’s the syntax

public static int parseInt(String s, int radix) throws NumberFormatException

Let’s see java program.

public class ConvertHexToDecimal
{
   public static void main(String[] args)
   {
      String strHex = "b";
      int decimal = Integer.parseInt(strHex, 16);
      System.out.println("Decimal number : " + decimal);
   }
}


Output:

Decimal number : 11
